data.chText: 水下的；用于水下的；水下发生的
data.enText: found, used or happening below the surface of water

data.chText: 深吸一口气，看你能在水里待多久。
data.enText: Take a deep breath and see how long you can stay underwater.

example: viewing subaqueous fauna from a glass-bottomed boat

tr: beneath the surface of the water

value.def: Something that exists or happens underwater exists or happens below the surface of the sea, a river, or a lake.

example.ex: ...giant submarines able to travel at high speeds underwater...
example.tran: 能够在水下高速行进的巨型潜艇

example.ex: Some stretches of beach are completely underwater at high tide...
example.tran: 海滩上有些地方在涨潮时完全淹没在水中。

example.ex: State television showed film of vast areas of farmland underwater.
example.tran: 国家电视台播出了大片农田淹没在水中的影像。

value.def: Underwater devices are specially made so that they can work in water.

example.ex: ...a pool of clear water lit by underwater lights.
example.tran: 被水下灯光照亮的一池碧水

trans: 水下混凝土；水中混凝土
水下机器人；水下機器人
水下照相机，防水照相机
